
[1]cuckold

   CUCKOLD, n. A man whose wife is false to his bed; the husband of an
   adulteress.

   CUCKOLD, v.t.

   1. To make a man a cuckold by criminal conversation with his wife;
   applied to the seducer.

   2. To make a husband a cuckold by criminal conversation with another
   man; applied to the wife.
